 Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id ibn al-Mu\u2019alla reported: I was praying in the mosque when the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, called out to me but I did not respond. I said later, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I was praying.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cDid not Allah say: Respond to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25144,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/08\/09\/dua-nawm-waking-up\/","url_meta":{"origin":33170,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet\u2019s supplication for sleep, waking up","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, laid down at night, he would place his hand under his cheek and then say, \u201cO Allah, in Your name I die and I live.\u201d When the Prophet would awaken, he would say, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25901,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/05\/dua-wake-up-in-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":33170,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication to say when waking up in night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever wakes up in the night and says, 'There is no God but Allah, alone without any partner. To Him belong the dominion and all praise, and He has power over all things. All praise is due\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33170","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=33170"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33170\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=33170"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=33170"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=33170"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}